### 1.1.0 - 2026-03-04

- Add adapter architecture with separate Node and Expo SQLite adapters
- Add React Native entrypoint and Expo-focused API (`src/expo.js`)
- Add forward city search and stable `geonames:<id>` identifiers
- Update GeoNames generation schema + indexes for forward/reverse lookups
- Add test coverage for reverse, forward, stable-id find, schema indexes, and Expo adapter execution

### 1.0.0 - 2018-08-02

- Add bug fix for reverse lookup in rural/remote areas (@cosorio94)
- Upgrade sqlite3 to fix compatability issues with Node v10

### 0.0.1 - 2016-05-05

- Initial release
